title: RHONJ Take Me Out to the Ball Game ⚾️
itunes:title: RHONJ Take Me Out to the Ball Game ⚾️
description:
Danny recaps The Real Housewives of New Jersey, which saw the women channeling their inner Rockford Peaches/Paterson Peaches, with a charity softball game. There was also legging drama, and more in a delightful episode (IMO)! No RHOC this week as Danny is a little under the weather and didn't get to watch the episode in time, but he will return next week!
